            <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 10 月 29 日消息，小米 15 手机今日正式发布，特别的亮银版<strong>定价 4699 元起</strong>，相比普通版贵了 200 元。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="517" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/4a53b609-0378-49f2-ac4c-2d00137b9598.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="4699 元起，小米 15 亮银版手机发布" width="1190" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="502" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/137705ca-b44d-4c16-8d4e-c059414cf8f3.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="4699 元起，小米 15 亮银版手机发布" width="1440" /></p><p>亮银配色曾在小米 6、小米 10 至尊纪念版手机上推出，也是小米旗舰手机的经典配色。</p><p>据介绍，小米 15 手机亮银版“<strong>首创铝金属高亮工艺</strong>”，重量仅为不锈钢的 1/3。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="365" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/d0b676ee-8cc9-4c0b-b33a-bc4657061d33.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="4699 元起，小米 15 亮银版手机发布" width="1440" /></p><p>该机背板采用&nbsp;<strong>3D 热弯玻璃</strong>，打造“真实波浪触感”，IT之家附官方渲染图如下：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1093" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/a3fa3745-c8bf-4686-a627-297a7ae63ab9.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="4699 元起，小米 15 亮银版手机发布" width="1440" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1093" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/819039a5-e9f9-4340-b500-8b45572a12ac.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="4699 元起，小米 15 亮银版手机发布" width="1440" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1093" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/87236d40-f676-48a6-8a32-9f0a20f51485.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="4699 元起，小米 15 亮银版手机发布" width="1440" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1093" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/054921c5-ca4d-4c2b-93ce-36b2f722eb47.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="4699 元起，小米 15 亮银版手机发布" width="1440" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1093" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/81f64725-f9ee-47b7-84cd-2c3f9f346189.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="4699 元起，小米 15 亮银版手机发布" width="1440" /></p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/KrypfH1" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/157009/28/50273/46833/67203b98F54771073/6a5ba88e31a81d66.jpg" title="4699 元起，小米 15 亮银版手机发布" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">小米 15 亮银版</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 4699 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p><ul class="small-size list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>《<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/806/219.htm" target="_blank">4499 元起小米 15 手机正式发布：骁龙 8 至尊版、12GB 内存起步、超声波指纹</a>》</p></li></ul><p>2024 年 11.11 大促全网好价合集：<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fcontentlist%3Fapi%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnapi.ithome.com%252Fapi%252Ftopmenu%252Fgetmenufeeds%252F166%252F0%252Fnone%252F0%26title%3D2024%25E5%258F%258C11%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BF%2583%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E9%2580%2589%26mode%3D0" target="_blank" title="点此查看">点此查看</a></p><p><span class="font-color-red"><strong>京东无门槛红包&nbsp;</strong></span>至高 11111 元：<a href="https://u.jd.com/CaQySbH" target="_blank" title="点此抽今日红包"><strong>点此抽今日红包</strong></a></p><p><span class="font-color-orangered"><strong>天猫无门槛红包&nbsp;</strong></span>至高 24888 元：<strong><a href="https://s.click.taobao.com/w26hFPt" target="_blank">点此抽今日红包</a></strong></p><p><span class="font-color-purple"><strong>唯品会无门槛红包</strong></span> 至高1111元：<a href="https://t.vip.com/VbMVne" target="_blank"><strong>点此抽今日红包</strong></a></p><p><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a class="topic-bar" href="https://www.ithome.com/zt/xiaomi15/" target="_blank">Xiaomi 15 系列暨小米澎湃 OS 2 新品发布会专